    <subfield code="m">It is worth noting that the lower bound (12) on the angular eigenvalues can be saturated in the eikonal l = m ≫ 1 limit, in which case one finds the simple relation Kmm = m2 [1 + O(m-1 )] - a2 (µ2 - ω2 ) [26]</subfield>
