  <datafield tag="999" ind1="C" ind2="5">
    <subfield code="m">It is worth emphasizing again that these stationary (marginally-stable) scalar field configurations are characterized by the marginal (critical) frequency ωfield = ωc ≡ mΩH for superradiant scattering in the Kerr black-hole spacetime [see Eq. (4)]</subfield>
    <subfield code="o">34</subfield>
